parameters: "Let's go work part-time at the Jagged Mart!"
"Beautiful Student Council President Memimi\nSameyama! What's her secret side...?"

A place where ordinary people cannot enter, an underground
arena. At the heart of the frenzy, monstrous gladiators face
off in the ring. This is the venue for illegal betting
matches, "Monster Fight."

Brachiocondor: Gwahahaha-! Your winning streak ends here!!
I'll be taking over your organization's territory!!

A monstrous figure, likely over three meters tall, roars.
The one showered with this terrifying voice is a petite
girl, seemingly ill-suited for battle.

Shark Broccoli: No need to bark... The victor will be me...
You shall become the foundation of our organization!

This is Dorietoku City. Due to the corruption of
administrative organizations, it has become a lawless zone.
In the underworld of this city with a population of about
100,000... countless illegal organizations are writhing.

To avoid large-scale conflicts when disputes arise... each
organization sends out their strongest member to fight one-
on-one in the ring, staking their pride and rights against
each other.

Audience: Hehehe, this time for sure, that Shark girl is
done for!! Brachiocondor is the heaviest among all monsters!
I've bet 100,000 on her loss... this time it's a sure thing!

Audience: Shark Broccoli is now a hotshot monster with real
talent. Even against the veteran Brachiocondor with 25
undefeated battles, it won't be an easy win! We're in for an
amazing fight!

The audience members are all people living in the city's
underworld. They act as mediators in organizational
conflicts and are gamblers who keep the city's dark economy
turning through their bets.

Bunny-chan: The match starts in 10 seconds~❤︎ Both fighters,
do your best♪

With their well-trained bodies carrying the fate of their
organizations... the monsters fight tonight to push their
own organizations to the top...
